{"tid":1922291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"因《反蒙面法》 奧地利戴口罩需醫生證明　違者重罰150歐元","createTime":"2020-03-12T13:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T15:58:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f6e3d126e6d80f4872e0d09780037ae9ae401a","tid":1922291,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2585000/2588511/P5_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2585000%2F2588511%2FP5_600.jpg&h=90ee51f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17:00 2020/03/12<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情繼續肆虐全球，歐洲多個國家感染人數直綫上升。為了避免疫情繼續蔓延，歐洲的人民外出都開始戴上口罩。然而，奧地利卻因為《反蒙面法》而嚴禁民眾戴口罩，違者將被罰150歐元（約1,300元）。<br />\n<br />\n截至周四（3月12日），奧地利累計確診案例已達246例。駐奧地利代表處表示，即使新冠病毒肆虐歐洲，但目前在奧地利公共場合隨便戴口罩仍屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n駐奧地利代表處指，奧地利從2017年10月1日起通過 《反蒙面法》在奧地利境內之公共場所，包括地鐵、公車、戲院、馬路上等，沒有合理理由便不能戴口罩等遮住臉部的物品，違耆可能被警察人員罰最高150歐元。<br />\n<br />\n奧地利內政部長及衛生部表示，政府將認真應對新冠肺炎，民眾毋須驚慌，在公共場合仍不用以防止感染為理由去配戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：林展鋒 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2588511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2588511&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=ce0d1ab2\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2588511</a>"},{"pid":"1831ab64876e22ff0115755d14d46fdd1b31af3a","tid":1922291,"uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"又申請做Failed State <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3ae234d7ea623584138b0b527ec47ef7212264","tid":1922291,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig